      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just doesn't feel temporary though. it feels like a fundamental truth. like the core was removed and what's left is just an empty vessel. how can i \"find my way back\" to a person who doesn't even exist anymore? if the music was the thing that made me real, and that's gone... then what am i actually doing here? it just feels like i'm performing the motions of being alive for no reason.",
